{"title":"如何将Kali系统装入U盘","date":"2019-05-17T03:18:58.000Z","slug":"如何将Kali系统装入U盘","updated":"2019-05-17T03:19:59.855Z","content":"<p>###1.软件下载</p>\n<p>1.<a href=\"https://rufus.ie/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Rufus</a>：一个可以帮助格式化和创建可引导USB闪存盘的工具，比如 USB 随身碟，记忆棒等等。</p>\n<p>2.Win32 Disk Imager</p>\n<p>3.Universal USB Installer</p>\n<p>4.Minitool Partition Wizard</p>\n<p>5.<a href=\"https://www.kali.org/downloads/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Kali Linux Images</a></p>\n<p>###2.</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">fdisk -l</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>列出所有分区表</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">fdisk /dev/sdb</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">n</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>新建分区</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">w</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>保存修改</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mkfs.ext4 -L persistence /dev/sdb3</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>格式化分区 -L 分区序号</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">e2label /dev/sdb3 persistence</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>查看或定义卷标</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mkdir -p /mnt/myusb</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>建立一个子目录，-p 确保目录名称存在，如果目录不存在的就新创建一个</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mount /dev/sdb3 /mnt/myusb</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>将分区挂接到Linux的一个文件夹下</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">echo &quot;/ union&quot; &gt;/mnt/myusb/persistence.conf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">umount /dev/sdb3 &amp;&amp; reboot</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>卸除文件系统</p>\n","prev":{"title":"Visual Studio Code通过SSH远程编辑文件","slug":"Visual-Studio-Code通过SSH远程编辑文件"},"next":{"title":"aircrack-ng破解wep、wpa、wpa2加密的wifi","slug":"aircrack-ng破解wep、wpa、wpa2加密的wifi"},"link":"http://yoursite.com/post/如何将Kali系统装入U盘/"}